      "message": "[info] Line 26: FallbackCloneBackoff is stateful but not internally synchronized: every method (schedule/timerFired/cancel) is only safe because all current callers hold conv-\u003emtx. Since this is a standalone public header, a future caller could easily use it without a lock and introduce a data race on delay_/scheduled_. Add a short doc comment stating that instances are not thread-safe and require external synchronization (the owning SyncedConversation::mtx), so the invariant is explicit.",
